item.description:
Come down and watch 3 big games of hard hitting/ free flowing/ high scoring Aussie Rules Football on a great fall afternoon, Bring the picnic blanket/deck chair, kick back and relax for a great spectacle. The Dees are pumped for 2 big wins and want your support! Barbie and refreshments available. Will be a great afternoon-guaranteed!

P.s. One of our aussie mates is starting up a meat pie company in Boston and will be bringing a batch of fresh pies for us to try during the games!
